body: I am still in awe of the fact that Taylor was able to commission a mural. Not announce it to anyone, give no mention of it to anyone, even her dad and people still were able to figure out she did it. And then a million people showed up at it. This is just a completely surreal thing and we don’t talk about it enough.

summary:
I am a big TS fan, and never really used Tumblr but I have nowhere else to post my crazy theories. Here a girl out ;)
So, I'm...
body:
Just another TS7 theory Part 1

I am a big TS fan, and never really used Tumblr but I have nowhere else to post my crazy theories. Here a girl out ;)

So, I’m thinking of possible Album names. I have 2. One thats pretty straight forward, and one that’s very in depth and might seem a bit farfetched but we all know Miss Swift never just gives things away.

I’ll start off with the shortest one.

1. KALEIDOSCOPE HEART.

Now we have all heard the theories about Kaleidoscope so I won’t touch base on that, but I watched a fellow YouTuber (I’ll paste the link below) who described a “heart” theory. She didn’t go into too much detail, pointing out that the theme of Hearts is very common throughout everything, but after also 2 hours of letting my husband get away with watching his TV shows that I found some more evidence.

So yes, there’s a lot of hearts in the video clip, Like Lauren touched based with, but let’s add these too.

Billboard awards 2018 was the first time we see Taylor in a Pastel coloured dress. And the post of her with BTS in that dress, she adds the 💗 emoji (the heart within a heart within a heart emoji. Just in case Tumblr doesn’t show the emoji I just added). Checking almost every post on Taylor’s instagram we have never really seen this heart before. It’s usually a solid red heart or the double hearts. Coincidences, I think not.

Oh and she did say on Ellen there’s an Easter egg during her interview. Taylor doesn’t seem to move her hands but made sure she did the love heart thing with her hands when she was talking about Benjamin Button. It could be it guys!

Check out Lauren for her theories too!

https://youtu.be/-nY7Sf9PmLs

Okay, this one I probably dug too deep into, so I could be grasping at straws but, hey it could be just a coincidence (…or I’m just totally over thinking it)

2. DIAMONDS. (What is the rainbows are actually the reflection you see from a diamond)

I’ll start off with some quick photographic evidence

🔹Diamond ring

🔹 diamonds in the rainbow

🔹 diamond fence holes

🔹 diamond photo within a photo frame thingamabob

🔹diamond tiles (now Taylor confirms that this particular scene has an Easter egg - Tiles perhaps, instead of the Palm trees?)

NOW for some more in depth ideas!

I got this idea from this Insta post.

There’s a circling theory that Taylor wore this dress, or dresses like this to signify her collar with Panic at the Discos Brendon Urie. And it got me thinking. If she got a DIAMOND award from Fearless, why did they use this photo? Was Taylor hinting that she’s going to continue to make great and hit high music awards from the new TS7. Like she was crowned a diamond award and now’s she’s showing us Why and that she can continue to do great things?

This leads me on to the other half of this theory.

This was written about why Taylor got the diamond award and the words “love” and “me” stand out. We have seen from Taylor’s ME video that it’s really a song about love, and it also touches on why someone should be in a relationship with her ( because she’s Awesome, Durr) and is very similar to “you belong with me”. So again, she’s trying to recreate greatness just like Fearless! Go girl!

Continued onto my next post to see more evidence

@taylorswift

summary: Okay, so I saw a post where people found out the background song from the Me! mv was a song called “La Vie En Rose” , and it had...
body:
Okay, so I saw a post where people found out the background song from the Me! mv was a song called “La Vie En Rose” , and it had a line that had something about seeing life through rose colored glasses (also the title translated into something similar to Life in Pink),, which got my thinking about all the pink clues Taylor had in the mv!! The pink snake at the beginning with the word colors on its side (the color pink!)

and then her pink hair and how she was WEARING ROSE COLORED GLASSES in the pic with the five holes in a fence, etc.

so i decided to look up the symbolism of rose colored glasses….

AND THE ORIGINAL PIC CAME UP!!

CHICKENS WORE ROSE COLORED GLASSES !!!

AND WHAT ARE THERE A BUNCH OF PHOTOS OF IN THE ME VIDEO?

A lot of cool chicks out there… with rose colored glasses??🤔🤔 @taylorswift

summary:
Ok, so I've got a theory even though that may be just me being crazy:
Taylor had blue hair during the Ellen interview and wore a...
body:
Ok, so I’ve got a theory even though that may be just me being crazy:

Taylor had blue hair during the Ellen interview and wore a blue dress. I was wondering “why doesn’t she have pink hair?” I mean: she dyed her hair pink to promote ME!, so who says she didn’t dye her hair blue to promote the other side of TS7? What if the album has a “pink side” (happy and funny songs) + a “blue side” (sad, nostalgic songs)? What if she tried to tell us through this small details?

As I said, maybe I could be wrong and she just had blue hair for fun or to show us that this era will be more colorful, but still I have this idea through my mind that’s killing me.

What do you think?
